snippet.title: Diana and Roma Save Christmas
snippet.description:
Diana and Roma have to save Christmas. Santa Claus has landed at their house and needs their help to repair his sleigh. Will Diana and Roma's family be able to save the day? Find out in this exciting Christmas video!

00:00 Diana and Roma save Christmas
04:18 Inflatable Pool Adventure
07:06 Diana and Roma Help Oliver Escape the Maze
